Package: fars
Title: Utility functions for the analysis of Fatality Analysis Reporting System files
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Giulia",
           family = "Pais",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "giuliapais1@gmail.com")
Description: Provides a set of utility functions to read and summarize  Fatality Analysis Reporting System files.
  It's possible to read sigle files given the path on disk or provide a year and construct a path for import.
  Summarizes operations comprise the count of accidents in a file grouped by year and month, and a plotting function
  is provided to better visualize the coordinates and density of accidents on a map.
